## UI DESIGN PRINCIPLES

- **Mobile-first.** This is a phone app used on job sites. Every tap target minimum 44px.
- **One-handed operation.** Primary actions at thumb reach (bottom of screen).
- **Dark mode default.** Trades people work in all lighting conditions.
- **Scan is the hero action.** Big camera button, always visible, bottom center.
- **Speed over features.** The flow is: tap вҶ’ snap вҶ’ done. OCR happens in background.
- **Forgiveness over precision.** OCR will get things wrong. Make every field editable with one tap.
- **MyPoorBrain branding.** Match PaintBrain's visual language вҖ” dark theme, accent colors from the MPB palette.

